      <b data-is-speakable>Michael Cohen Recorded A Conversation With Trump About Paying An Ex-Playboy Model</b>   <b data-is-speakable>The FBI found the secret recording after a raid on the lawyer's office in April. His lawyer says, "Suffice it to say that when the recording is heard, it will not hurt Mr. Cohen."</b>
